name: jowunX.1
description:
Jowun is the Commander of Orga Division, assigned to protect the 3 Krotep Stones guarded within the Great Kingdom, the same 3 stones coveted by the ruthless and cruel Veroun. Orga soldiers, trained from infancy, are known throughout the Binary Solar System for their fierce strength and unwavering loyalty in maintaining their duty.

Name : Jowun
Tribe : Orgasian
Planet : Shining Star
Weapon of Choice: Orga Sword
Religeon: Does not believe in any religion
